apps.localizedDescription:
Proof-of-concept app to overwrite fonts on iOS using CVE-2022-46689.

Works on iOS 16.1.2 and below (tested on iOS 16.1) on unjailbroken devices.
apps.name: WDBFontOverwrite
apps.subtitle: An alternative App Store for iOS.
apps.versionDescription:
Fonts included:

DejaVu Sans Condensed
DejaVu Serif
DejaVu Sans Mono
Go Regular
Go Mono
Fira Sans
Segoe UI
Comic Sans MS
Choco Cooky
You can also import custom fonts that were ported for iOS.

apps.localizedDescription:
A Jailed toolbox application for iOS 14.0-15.7.1 and 16.0-16.1.2 using CVE-2022-46689.

Enable Notifications and set Location Services to Always to keep the app running in the background, keep the dock and folder background hidden, and prevent some sound effects from reverting.

Warning: Some changes are permanent on iOS 14.0-14.8.1.
apps.name: Cowbunga
apps.subtitle: ToolBox For MacDirtyCow Tweaks
